        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tit</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ant</abbr><ex>onius</ex></expan> Pecu<lb break="no" n="3"/>liaris co<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>nd</abbr><ex>uctor</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vect</abbr><ex>igalis</ex></expan> oc<lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex cert="low">avi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>oniarum</ex></expan> II <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> XII
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Siegel; ungefähr kreisrund. Buchstaben linksläufig und spiegelverkehrt geschrieben. Buchstabe A ohne Querhaste. (B): Tóth: Z. 3/4: co/nductor; Z. 6: ann(o) conductionis XII. Es handelt sich wohl um dieselbe Person wie in der Bauinschrift CIL 03, 10495 =TitAq 0007 (= HD067843).</p>
            </div>
